@startuml
title Viaverse Admin / Moderation Action — Sequence Diagram

actor Admin
participant "Admin UI" as AdminUI
participant "Admin BFF" as BFF
participant "identity-service" as Identity
participant "admin-ops-service" as AdminOps
participant "Domain Service" as Domain
participant "audit-service" as Audit
database "PostgreSQL" as DB
queue "Outbox / Kafka" as Kafka

Admin -> AdminUI : submit moderation action
AdminUI -> BFF : POST /admin/actions
BFF -> Identity : validate admin session + MFA
Identity --> BFF : valid
BFF -> AdminOps : performAction(command)
AdminOps -> Identity : check permission/resource scope
Identity --> AdminOps : allowed
AdminOps -> Domain : apply moderation/domain action
Domain -> DB : update target state
Domain --> AdminOps : applied
AdminOps -> Audit : write audit log
Audit -> DB : append immutable audit record
AdminOps -> DB : store admin case/action
AdminOps -> Kafka : AdminActionApplied
Kafka --> AdminUI : case update / notification

note bottom
Admin BFF authenticates admin session.
admin-ops-service orchestrates action.
Domain service owns target state.
Audit is mandatory.
end note
@enduml
